sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Auth as Auth System
    participant IC as Item Controller
    participant ME as Matching Engine
    participant DB as Database
    participant NS as Notification Service

    rect rgb(245, 245, 245)
    Note over User, DB: Item Submission & Storage
    User->>Auth: Provide Credentials / Session Token
    activate Auth
    Auth-->>User: Authentication Success
    deactivate Auth

    User->>IC: Submit Item Report (Lost/Found)
    activate IC
    IC->>DB: Store Item Metadata
    activate DB
    DB-->>IC: Confirmation (Item_ID Created)
    deactivate DB
    
    IC->>ME: Initiate Matching Request (Item_ID)
    activate ME
    end

    rect rgb(235, 245, 255)
    Note over ME, NS: Background Matching Logic & Trigger
    ME->>DB: Retrieve Candidate Dataset (Category/Location)
    activate DB
    DB-->>ME: Return Potential Matches
    deactivate DB

    ME->>ME: Execute Comparison Logic (NLP/Attribute Filter)

    alt Match Found
        ME->>DB: Link Match IDs & Update Status
        ME->>NS: Trigger Match Notification
        activate NS
        NS-->>User: Alert: "Possible Match Found for your Item"
        
        Note right of NS: Parallel Alert to the corresponding Party
        NS-->>User: Alert: "A new item matches your report"
        deactivate NS
        
    else No Match Found
        ME-->>IC: Status: No Immediate Match
    end
    
    deactivate ME
    IC-->>User: Report Processed Successfully
    deactivate IC
    end